                                                                                  <h4>How we&#039;re holding the line in Virunga</h4>
                                        <div class="description-container">
                      We’re calling for all oil companies to stay out of Virunga National Park, and for the government to cancel all permits to explore for oil in the area.
                                                                      <div class="find-out-more-container">
                          <a href="">
                                                          Find out more
                                                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                                          </div>
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </li>
